<h1 class="team-member--name">Gary Russell</h1>
<div class="team-member--sub-info">
<p>Project Lead, Spring Integration, AMQP</p>
<p>Pennsylvania, USA</p>
</div>
<div class="team-member--bio">Gary has been in software engineering, concentrating on Enterprise Integration, for over 30 years on various platforms, and in the Java space since the late &#39;90s.
He has been developing with the Spring Framework since 2004.
He has been a committer on the Spring Integration and Spring AMQP projects for over 7 years. He leads both projects as well as the Spring for Apache Kafka project and is a co-lead on the Spring Cloud Stream project.</div>
</div>
</div>
